      <description>

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://i.imgur.com/tc7A3LK.png&#34; alt=&#34;OpposeInertia&#34; /&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Oppose Inertia was an experiment to make a 2D space combat game with a heavy focus on procedural generation. It never turned out exactly as I&amp;rsquo;d hoped but it was a good learning experience.
Explore star systems, each with unique enemies, which drop new weapons, abilities, or ship schematics for you to use.&lt;/p&gt;

